Strat tries to be smarter than Chaotic, the sample Risk player Mike Ferris supplied with version 0.95.  The code is in fact based on Chaotic, which I used as the shell for my first player, and just kept mutating until what you've got here.  There are too many details to go into, and I don't want to give away all of the elements of strategy to the idly curious, but here are some general features:\
\
